productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
It only works when I'm Nepal.
heard about this on instrumental country radio, decided to give it a try.
The box this comes in is 3 light-year by 5 meter and weights 10 ounce!
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
